  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hidden Oddities is a cosy hidden object game where you search in the nooks and crannies across lush miniature landscapes, it's amazing what you might find in some of the oddest of places. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A list of items shows you what you're looking at, hover over them for a closer look, and find enough to progress to the next location. <br><br><strong><u>Game Features</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 Levels and counting </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >87+ items to find </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non intrusive background music to relax to </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming gameplay with interactive elements </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for all ages!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983240/extras/d6a232f002d32f507d84cf4fbfb5ab40.poster.avif?t=1731602345\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983240/extras/d6a232f002d32f507d84cf4fbfb5ab40.webm?t=1731602345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983240/extras/d6a232f002d32f507d84cf4fbfb5ab40.mp4?t=1731602345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983240/extras/895eed479aa1b6ebcbc359e5f35e56d8.poster.avif?t=1731602345\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2983240/extras/895eed479aa1b6ebcbc359e5f35e56d8.webm?t=1731602345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor